&CP2K
 PROGRAM      Quickstep
 IOLEVEL      10
 FFTLIB       FFTSG
&END

&DFT
 FUNCTIONAL   Pade
 LSD
&END

&QS
 CUTOFF       140
 EPS_DEFAULT  1.0E-8
 RS_GRID DISTRIBUTED
&END

&SCF
 GUESS        atomic
 EPS_DIIS     0.1
 MAX_DIIS     4
 EPS_SCF      1.0E-4
 MAX_SCF      3
 MIXING       0.4
&END

&PRINT medium
&END

&KIND K
 BASIS_SET    DZVP-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH-PADE-q1
&END

&KIND H
 BASIS_SET    DZVP-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH-PADE-q1
&END

&CELL
 UNIT         ANGSTROM
 ABC          6.0 6.0 12.0  
&END

&COORD
 K     0.000000  0.000000  0.000000
 K     1.000000  0.000000  3.000000
 K     2.000000  2.000000  5.000000
 K     3.000000  2.000000  8.000000
 H     4.000000  0.000000  11.000000
 H     4.000000  1.000000  11.000000
&END
